<item><title>Water Tanker Services under an Open Panel Contract Arrangement</title>
<description><![CDATA[<b>Tender Details : </b> The City of Greater Bendigo (City) invites submissions from suitably experienced and equipped Contractors for the provision of water tanker/water cart services, including delivery and water application, typically for road construction and unsealed road maintenance with the enter Greater Bendigo Municipal area.<br /><br />Other services relating to Water Tanker/Water Cart operations may be requested from time to time, including watering trees, flushing drains and emergency management support.<br /><br />Refer to uploaded tender documents for full details.<br /><br /><b>Issued by : </b> Greater Bendigo City Council<br /><b>Closing Date</b> : 28/Jul/2026 03:00 PM (UTC+10:00) Canberra, Melbourne, Sydney time<br /><b>Reference number</b> : VP515237<br /><b>Contact person</b> : Not disclosed<br /><b>Tender categories</b> : Plant & Equipment - Hire<br /><b>Specification Docs</b> : 4]]></description>
