<description><![CDATA[<b>Tender Details : </b> Flinders Shire Council invites tenders from suitably qualified tenderers for appointment as a Pre-Qualified Supplier of Trade Services for the categories of trade services.<br /><br />The categories include: <br /><br />Air Conditioning Maintenance & Services, Building – General Building Works, Carpentry – General (licensed – QBCC), Concreting - General concreting works (licensed - QBCC), Electrical – General, Electrical – Industrial, Electrical – Testing, Fencing (licensed – QBCC), Fencing (other works), Floor Coverings, Glazing, Handyperson Services, Landscaping, Lift Maintenance, Locksmith, Metal Fabrication & Welding (Mobile & Workshop), Painting, Pest Control, Plumbing, Plumbing (gas), Pressure Cleaning, Security Services & Monitoring, Soil Testing Services, Survey and Design Works, Underground Services Locator, Workshop Mechanic Services.<br /><br /><b>Issued by : </b> Flinders Shire Council<br /><b>Closing Date</b> : 27/Jul/2026 08:00 AM (UTC+10:00) Brisbane time<br /><b>Reference number</b> : VP515690<br /><b>Contact person</b> : Not disclosed<br /><b>Tender categories</b> : Building Trade, Repairs, Maint., Mechanical Plant, Equip, Services<br /><b>Specification Docs</b> : 7]]></description>
