<item><title>Provision of Roadside Advertising at Tora Street and Holland Park West</title>
<description><![CDATA[<b>Tender Details : </b> TMR manages commercial advertising agreements for third-party billboard and other out-of-home advertising devices across state-controlled road sites, busways and other transport infrastructure. Through this Invitation, TMR seeks a suitably qualified and experienced Supplier to supply, install, maintain and operate roadside advertising devices at the Tora Street overpass and at Holland Park West.<br /><br />The scope of the opportunity is to:<br /><br />- supply, install, maintain and operate two static digital advertising billboards on the Tora Street overpass over Road ID U28B (Bridge ID 19940), at MacGregor, Queensland 4109, with one sign facing the northbound direction and one sign facing the southbound direction; and<br /><br />- supply, install, maintain and operate one single-sided static digital advertising billboard located in the State Road Corridor opposite Holland Park West Busway Station.<br /><br />The Advertising Assets are likely to be greater than 4m² and must conform to TMR roadside advertisi...<br /><br /><b>Issued by : </b> Department of Transport and Main Roads<br /><b>Closing Date</b> : 17/Aug/2026 05:00 PM (UTC+10:00) Brisbane time<br /><b>Reference number</b> : VP515606<br /><b>Contact person</b> : Not disclosed<br /><b>Tender categories</b> : Advertising and Media Services, Signs & Barriers<br /><b>Specification Docs</b> : 6]]></description>
