<item><title>IRC-IS-0526-T476 Regional LED Lighting Renewal and Upgrade Program 2026-27</title>
<description><![CDATA[<b>Tender Details : </b> Isaac Regional Council (Council) is seeking to engage a suitably qualified contractor to undertake investigation, assessment, design, and/or upgrade works across multiple lighting infrastructure projects within the Isaac Regional Council area.<br /><br />The projects aim to improve public safety, usability, energy efficiency, asset reliability, and compliance with relevant Australian Standards through renewal and upgrade of existing lighting infrastructure at sporting facilities, aquatic centres, and public open spaces.<br /><br />The RFT includes the following projects:<br /><br />Project 1 - Dysart Rugby League Lighting Renewal Design<br /><br />Design for renewal and upgrade of sporting field lighting infrastructure at Hickey Oval, Dysart Rugby League facility.<br /><br />Project 2 - Floodlight LED Upgrades at Glenden, Clermont, and Middlemount swimming pools<br /><br />Design and Installation of LED floodlight upgrades at Glenden, Clermont, and Middlemount swimming pools.<br /><br />Project 3 - Moranbah P...<br /><br /><b>Issued by : </b> Isaac Regional Council<br /><b>Closing Date</b> : 27/Jul/2026 02:00 PM (UTC+10:00) Brisbane time<br /><b>Reference number</b> : VP515632<br /><b>Contact person</b> : Not disclosed<br /><b>Tender categories</b> : Building Trade, Repairs, Maint., ELEC, Lighting, Equip & Services<br /><b>Specification Docs</b> : 8]]></description>
