<item><title>Online Instrument Calibration, Maintenance and Repair</title>
<description><![CDATA[<b>Tender Details : </b> The calibration, maintenance and repair (scheduled and unplanned) of online instruments located at twenty-one (21) MidCoast Council operational sites and seventeen (17) MidCoast Council reservoir sites. The prescribed works will commence on 1 August 2026 for a period of two (2) years. The works prescribe the instrument types, locations and appropriate service regimes based on manufacturer and/or operational requirements. The work covers all aspects of instrument maintenance, calibration and repair including the supply of generic consumables. Specialist Original Equipment Manufacturer (OEM) components and consumables are excluded from the Specification with the procurement of these items subject to negotiation with the successful contractor.<br /><br /><b>Issued by : </b> MidCoast Council<br /><b>Closing Date</b> : 24/Jul/2026 05:00 PM (UTC+10:00) Canberra, Melbourne, Sydney time<br /><b>Reference number</b> : VP515471<br /><b>Contact person</b> : Not disclosed<br /><b>Tender categories</b> : Building Trade, Repairs, Maint., Lab, Measure, Observe & Test Equip, Water & Sewage<br /><b>Specification Docs</b> : 10]]></description>
