<item><title>Waste Management Centre Cell 5 Construction</title>
<description><![CDATA[<b>Tender Details : </b> Council is seeking Submissions from appropriately qualified and experienced Tenderers for the construction of Waste Management Centre Cell 5, including all civil, geotechnical, environmental protection and associated works required to deliver the new landfill cell.<br /><br />Successful delivery of the project requires:<br /><br /> - Completion of Cell 5 in accordance with approved design, statutory requirements, contract documentation and contract timeframe<br /><br /> - Safe construction with effective WHS management and environmental controls.<br /><br /> - Delivery within approved budget and program.<br /><br /> - Integration of leachate, groundwater, drainage and environmental protection systems.<br /><br /> - A constructed asset capable of operational use and regulatory compliance.<br /><br />Further details are seen in tender documents available for download.<br /><br /><b>Issued by : </b> Kempsey Shire Council<br /><b>Closing Date</b> : 28/Jul/2026 02:00 PM (UTC+10:00) Canberra, Melbourne, Sydney time<br /><b>Reference number</b> : VP515374<br /><b>Contact person</b> : Not disclosed<br /><b>Tender categories</b> : Construction & Operation, Water & Sewage<br /><b>Specification Docs</b> : 5]]></description>
