<item><title>Supply and Installation of Solar PV and Battery Storage for Three Council Sites</title>
<description><![CDATA[<b>Tender Details : </b> Oberon Council invites quotations for the design, supply, installation and commissioning of solar PV systems across three sites, including a VPP-compatible solar and battery system at the Water Treatment Plant (total 82kW solar and 250kWh battery capacity).<br /><br />The successful contractor will deliver a complete turnkey solution, including approvals, documentation and STC processing, with systems to be fully operational by December 2026.<br /><br />Council intends to appoint a single contractor for all sites (however may consider multiple contractors), with submissions to include site-specific pricing and demonstrated experience in similar projects. ChargeWorks has been engaged as technical advisor and will support project delivery.<br /><br /><b>Issued by : </b> Oberon Council<br /><b>Closing Date</b> : 31/Jul/2026 04:00 PM (UTC+10:00) Canberra, Melbourne, Sydney time<br /><b>Reference number</b> : VP514910<br /><b>Contact person</b> : Not disclosed<br /><b>Tender categories</b> : ELEC, Lighting, Equip & Services, Electronic Components & Supplies, Utilities<br /><b>Specification Docs</b> : 1]]></description>
