<pubDate>Fri, 19 Jun 2026 04:11:00 GMT</pubDate>
<category>Security Services &amp; Equipment</category>
</item>
<item><title>Head Contractor - Pimpama State School – New Tuckshop (With Design Responsibility)</title>
<description><![CDATA[<b>Tender Details : </b> Please contact Shay Lister – Project Manager on shay@honeywill.com.au with your company details and tender documentation will be emailed to contractors. Details of the site inspection will be advised in the email and letters to tenderers.<br /><br />The Department of Education (DoE) is calling for tender submissions for the construction of a New Tuckshop at Pimpama State School, located at 9 Hotham Creek Road, Pimpama QLD 4209, as part of the Capital Works (CAPITAL WORKS) program.<br /><br />The scope comprises a new free-standing Tuckshop. The position of the new building is centrally located on the school site with limited site access and working space. All works are to be completed by the end of February 2026.<br /><br />Tender submissions will be accepted from contractors that meet the following requirements:<br /><br />•	Appropriate QBCC Builders licences to undertake the entire scope of works<br /><br />•	Professional Indemnity Insurance to the value of $ 1M<br /><br />Minimum PQC Level 2 Eligibility re...<br /><br /><b>Issued by : </b> Department of Education<br /><b>Closing Date</b> : 17/Jul/2026 02:00 PM (UTC+10:00) Brisbane time<br /><b>Reference number</b> : VP513995<br /><b>Contact person</b> : Not disclosed<br /><b>Tender categories</b> : Building Trade, Repairs, Maint., Construction & Operation<br /><b>Specification Docs</b> : 0]]></description>
