<item><title>Supplier Onboarding and Supplier Payment</title>
<description><![CDATA[<b>Tender Details : </b> The University of Southern Queensland (UniSQ) is seeking to procure a Supplier Onboarding, Identity Verification and Banking Validation Solution, including implementation, integration, training, and ongoing support services. <br /><br />The solution is required to address current challenges in supplier onboarding and master data management, including manual validation processes, fragmented workflows, and limited automated controls, which present risks relating to fraud, duplicate records, and inaccurate supplier data. <br /><br />The proposed solution must enhance supplier identity verification, banking validation, data integrity, and ongoing change controls while ensuring compliance with audit, governance, and regulatory obligations.<br /><br /><b>Issued by : </b> University of Southern Queensland<br /><b>Closing Date</b> : 10/Jul/2026 05:00 PM (UTC+10:00) Brisbane time<br /><b>Reference number</b> : VP513993<br /><b>Contact person</b> : Not disclosed<br /><b>Tender categories</b> : IT & Telecomms<br /><b>Specification Docs</b> : 5]]></description>
