<item><title>CN25207 - Waste Collection Services</title>
<description><![CDATA[<b>Tender Details : </b> Noosa Shire Council invites suitably capable and experienced respondents to submit a Tender for the delivery of its next Waste Collection Services contract. Noosa Shire Council services a resident population of approximately 59,274 and receives in excess of 2.1 million visitors annually, resulting in a service environment that is highly dynamic and variable.<br /><br />The contract encompasses the full delivery of waste collection services across the Noosa Shire region, including: <br /><br />Domestic Services: General waste (refuse) collection; Commingled recycling collection; Garden organic (green waste) collection.<br /><br />Commercial and Public Services: Commercial refuse, commingled recycling and cardboard collection; Public place bin services; Waste transfer station bin services; Bulk bin services associated with Council facilities.<br /><br />This procurement represents a significant, long-term service partnership, for the delivery of essential waste collection services across the Noosa Shire, includ...<br /><br /><b>Issued by : </b> Noosa Council<br /><b>Closing Date</b> : 10/Aug/2026 02:00 PM (UTC+10:00) Brisbane time<br /><b>Reference number</b> : VP513348<br /><b>Contact person</b> : Not disclosed<br /><b>Tender categories</b> : Waste Management & Landfill<br /><b>Specification Docs</b> : 9]]></description>
