</item>
<item><title>RFQ 260122 - Leak Detection at CHRC Aquatic Centres</title>
<description><![CDATA[<b>Tender Details : </b> The Central Highlands Regional Council invites submissions from suitably qualified and experienced contractors to undertake detailed inspections of multiple aquatic centres across the Central Highlands region. The scope of works includes the assessment of pools, balance tanks, and associated infrastructure to identify and report on any leaks, defects and structural deterioration.<br /><br />Locations are:<br /><br />•	Emerald Aquatic Centre – 62 Opal Street Emerald<br /><br />•	Blackwater Aquatic Centre – 51 Hunter Street Blackwater<br /><br />•	Rolleston Aquatic Centre – Meteor Street Rolleston<br /><br />•	Capella Aquatic Centre – Rickert St Capella<br /><br />•	Sapphire Aquatic Centre – 925 Anakie Sapphire Road Sapphire<br /><br /><b>Issued by : </b> Central Highlands Regional Council<br /><b>Closing Date</b> : 07/Jul/2026 05:00 PM (UTC+10:00) Brisbane time<br /><b>Reference number</b> : VP513373<br /><b>Contact person</b> : Not disclosed<br /><b>Tender categories</b> : Gas Energy, Infrastructure, Equipment, Sport, Recreation Equip, Services<br /><b>Specification Docs</b> : 3]]></description>
