<pubDate>Mon, 15 Jun 2026 05:46:00 GMT</pubDate>
<category>Business &amp; Administrative Services</category>
<category>Management Advisory Services</category>
</item>
<item><title>Boigu Aerodrome Reseal</title>
<description><![CDATA[<b>Tender Details : </b> Torres Strait Island Regional Council invites tenders from suitably qualified tenderers for the reseal of the Aerodrome Pavement <br /><br />on Boigu Island, as described in more detail in Part 5 – Scope. <br /><br />The works required under the Contract includes, however, is not limited to: <br /><br />• Site Establishment and Disestablishment. <br /><br />• Environmental Management <br /><br />• Demolition and removal of vegetation and debris at the surrounding pavement areas <br /><br />• Crack repair and remediation of existing pavement defects. <br /><br />• Supply and installation of two coat seal. <br /><br />• Supply and installation of pavement markings. <br /><br />• Testing of the pavement surface in accordance with the design report and specifications.<br /><br /><b>Issued by : </b> Torres Strait Island Regional Council<br /><b>Closing Date</b> : 08/Jul/2026 03:00 PM (UTC+10:00) Brisbane time<br /><b>Reference number</b> : VP513356<br /><b>Contact person</b> : Not disclosed<br /><b>Tender categories</b> : Construction & Operation<br /><b>Specification Docs</b> : 10]]></description>
