<item><title>Degassing of Refrigerators and Air Conditioners at the BRRC</title>
<description><![CDATA[<b>Tender Details : </b> Byron Shire Council receives approximately 1000 gassed refrigerators and air conditioners from the general public and commercial sources. Council requires a contractor to degas end-of-life refrigerators and air conditioners at the Byron Resource Recovery Centre at 117 The Manse Road, Myocum, in accordance with national regulation and Council requirements.<br /><br />Degassing is only to be conducted on weekdays between 8.00am and 3.30pm.<br /><br /><b>Issued by : </b> Byron Shire Council<br /><b>Closing Date</b> : 07/Jul/2026 02:00 PM (UTC+10:00) Canberra, Melbourne, Sydney time<br /><b>Reference number</b> : VP512974<br /><b>Contact person</b> : Not disclosed<br /><b>Tender categories</b> : Building Trade, Repairs, Maint., Mechanical Plant, Equip, Services<br /><b>Specification Docs</b> : 1]]></description>
