<item><title>Register of Pre-Qualified Suppliers (Refresh) - Trade Services</title>
<description><![CDATA[<b>Tender Details : </b> The Request for Tender constitutes a refresh of Council’s existing Register of Pre-Qualified Suppliers for Trade Services (HSC 25/11)<br /><br />The refresh is being undertaken to:<br /><br />• Provide additional opportunities for local suppliers to be included on the Register; and<br /><br />• Introduce an additional category of trades to better meet operational requirements.<br /><br />Suppliers successfully appointed through this refresh will be added to the existing Register and will be bound by the same Contract terms and expiry date.<br /><br />Hinchinbrook Shire Council invites tenders from suitably qualified tenderers for appointment as a pre-qualified supplier of trade services for the categories of trade services identified in the Scope.<br /><br />The initial term of the appointment is two (2) years with 1 x one year extension option.<br /><br /><b>Issued by : </b> Hinchinbrook Shire Council<br /><b>Closing Date</b> : 06/Jul/2026 02:00 PM (UTC+10:00) Brisbane time<br /><b>Reference number</b> : VP513280<br /><b>Contact person</b> : Not disclosed<br /><b>Tender categories</b> : Building Trade, Repairs, Maint., Construction & Operation, Mechanical Plant, Equip, Services<br /><b>Specification Docs</b> : 7]]></description>
