<item><title>Tender 89-24 RPQS Traffic Management Services REFRESH</title>
<description><![CDATA[<b>Tender Details : </b> GRC requires regular supply of traffic control and traffic management planning services and is seeking to establish arrangements with Service Providers for:<br /><br />- Traffic control services – including scheduled, short notice/emergency response; and<br /><br />- Traffic management planning services – including Traffic Management Plans (TMPs), Traffic Guidance Schemes (TGSs) and Traffic Management Designs (TMDs).<br /><br />GRC has appointed one Service Provider as the primary provider and multiple Service Providers as secondary providers. <br /><br />To meet GRC’s requirements for the above services, GRC is seeking offers from new Service Providers to be added to the list of secondary providers.<br /><br /><b>Issued by : </b> Gladstone Regional Council<br /><b>Closing Date</b> : 07/Jul/2026 02:00 PM (UTC+10:00) Brisbane time<br /><b>Reference number</b> : VP513135<br /><b>Contact person</b> : Not disclosed<br /><b>Tender categories</b> : Parking, Traffic Services & Equip, Signs & Barriers<br /><b>Specification Docs</b> : 2]]></description>
