<description><![CDATA[<b>Tender Details : </b> Aurukun Shire Council invites Tenders from suitably qualified Tenderers for Construction of two new dwellings (3-bedroom unit +1 bedroom unit) on 178 Muttich Street (demolition by others) as described in more detail in Part 5 – Scope. <br /><br /> <br /><br />This first project forms parts of a much larger program of dwelling construction to help address housing needs in Aurukun. This program will include a mixture of separate dwellings and dual occupancies on existing parcels of land. In the coming months it is anticipated that the construction of various packages of several homes will be offered for tendering. In addition, Council will commence construction of 69 new residential lots in the coming months. They too will require new dwellings in the future.<br /><br /><b>Issued by : </b> Aurukun Shire Council<br /><b>Closing Date</b> : 15/Jul/2026 05:00 PM (UTC+10:00) Brisbane time<br /><b>Reference number</b> : VP513051<br /><b>Contact person</b> : Not disclosed<br /><b>Tender categories</b> : Construction & Operation<br /><b>Specification Docs</b> : 20]]></description>
