<item><title>Environmental Controls Review</title>
<description><![CDATA[<b>Tender Details : </b> The City of Greater Bendigo (The City) is undertaking a two-stage review of the environmental planning controls, the Environmental Controls Review (ECR), to implement recommendations from the 2022 Greater Bendigo Planning Scheme Review.<br /><br />Stage 1 will review existing planning controls, native vegetation protection strategies, the urban–forest interface, and the protection of biolinks, and will make recommendations. Stage 2 will be undertaken internally and will incorporate the Stage 1 recommendations into the Greater Bendigo Planning Scheme (GBPS).<br /><br />Please refer to uploaded documents for full details.<br /><br /><b>Issued by : </b> Greater Bendigo City Council<br /><b>Closing Date</b> : 09/Jul/2026 05:00 PM (UTC+10:00) Canberra, Melbourne, Sydney time<br /><b>Reference number</b> : VP512777<br /><b>Contact person</b> : Not disclosed<br /><b>Tender categories</b> : Architecture, Design, Planning, Environmental & Heritage Services<br /><b>Specification Docs</b> : 3]]></description>
