<item><title>IRC-CS-0426-EOI472 EOI Management of Dysart Recreation Centre</title>
<description><![CDATA[<b>Tender Details : </b> Dear Sir/Madam, <br /><br />Isaac Regional Council is seeking Expressions of Interest to manage Dysart Recreation Centre located at 29 Queen Elizabeth Drive, Dysart.<br /><br />The scope of management includes all areas of the facility, excluding the gym.<br /><br />The successful respondent will develop and coordinate a range of services, programs, activities and events that are flexible, culturally inclusive and aim to build skills, provide knowledge, promote personal and social development, promote physical well-being, and create and sustain local networks.<br /><br />If you require an inspection of the facility it can be arranged by messaging through VendorPanel with a couple of proposed dates and times.<br /><br />Kind Regards, <br /><br />Isaac Regional Council<br /><br /><b>Issued by : </b> Isaac Regional Council<br /><b>Closing Date</b> : 17/Jul/2026 02:00 PM (UTC+10:00) Brisbane time<br /><b>Reference number</b> : VP512390<br /><b>Contact person</b> : Not disclosed<br /><b>Tender categories</b> : Sport, Recreation Equip, Services, Training & Development, Travel & Tourism<br /><b>Specification Docs</b> : 3]]></description>
