<item><title>Crescent Head Holiday Parks Surfside Amenities Refurbishment</title>
<description><![CDATA[<b>Tender Details : </b> The current toilet block is showing signs of age, it is 50 years plus old, there is some deterioration of <br /><br />the building fabric including minor spalling of brickwork and some timber rot though not suspected of <br /><br />being detrimental to the building’s structural adequacy. The fit out, cubicle doors, wash benches and <br /><br />tapware are in poor condition and are in need of replacement. The floor and wall tiles have been <br /><br />patched in the past and though functional, is not the best look for the park<br /><br />There is a non-mandatory site inspection scheduled for 22/06/2026 at 10am.<br /><br /><b>Issued by : </b> Kempsey Shire Council<br /><b>Closing Date</b> : 10/Jul/2026 02:00 PM (UTC+10:00) Canberra, Melbourne, Sydney time<br /><b>Reference number</b> : VP512163<br /><b>Contact person</b> : Not disclosed<br /><b>Tender categories</b> : Construction & Operation<br /><b>Specification Docs</b> : 3]]></description>
