<pubDate>Wed, 27 May 2026 05:04:00 GMT</pubDate>
<category>Construction &amp; Operation</category>
<category>Marine Transp. Products &amp; Services</category>
</item>
<item><title>Management and Operation of Barnwell Park Golf Course and Pro Shop</title>
<description><![CDATA[<b>Tender Details : </b> Tenders are invited from suitably qualified and experienced service providers for the Management and Operation of Barnwell Park Golf Course and Pro Shop.<br /><br />The scope of services requires the coordination, supervision and management of the use of the golf course, including:<br /><br />Collecting Green Fees<br /><br />Administering, implementing and observing adherence to Council Policies with regard to the management and conduct of activities on the Golf Course.<br /><br />Coordinating, supervising and managing Golf Course Use, as directed by the Lessor, including but not limited to:<br /><br />- The supervision of the playing of golf on the Golf Course. <br /><br />- Arranging bookings for play on the Golf Course. <br /><br />- Generally supervising the proper and efficient conduct, control and use of the Golf Course.<br /><br />- Keeping accurate statistics on total number of rounds, categories of concessional fees granted, and any other information required by Council.<br /><br />Please see attache...<br /><br /><b>Issued by : </b> City of Canada Bay Council<br /><b>Closing Date</b> : 07/Jul/2026 02:00 PM (UTC+10:00) Canberra, Melbourne, Sydney time<br /><b>Reference number</b> : VP511080<br /><b>Contact person</b> : Not disclosed<br /><b>Tender categories</b> : Sport, Recreation Equip, Services<br /><b>Specification Docs</b> : 3]]></description>
