<item><title>Miami Arts Depot - Expression of Interest</title>
<description><![CDATA[<b>Tender Details : </b> The Miami Arts Depot represents a rare and catalytic opportunity to shape the future of the Gold Coast’s creative economy. Positioned at the intersection of screen production, digital arts, and emerging creative technologies, the project seeks to transform an underutilised site into a vibrant, industry-led hub that supports high-value creative production and collaboration, alongside residential and commercial opportunities.<br /><br />Council is inviting Expressions of Interest from suitably qualified and experienced development partners to bring this vision to life. Through this process, Council is seeking innovative and commercially viable proposals that demonstrate design excellence, operational credibility, and a strong alignment with the strategic ambition of the precinct. Respondents are encouraged to propose bold yet deliverable solutions that maximise the site’s potential and deliver long-term economic and social value for the Gold Coast.<br /><br />The City of Gold Coast (the City) has made the Miami...<br /><br /><b>Issued by : </b> Invest Gold Coast<br /><b>Closing Date</b> : 31/Jul/2026 10:00 PM (UTC+10:00) Brisbane time<br /><b>Reference number</b> : VP507384<br /><b>Contact person</b> : Not disclosed<br /><b>Tender categories</b> : Real Estate & Property Services<br /><b>Specification Docs</b> : 6]]></description>
