<item><title>Preventative Mechanical Maintenance Services</title>
<description><![CDATA[<b>Tender Details : </b> Federation University operates across multiple campuses comprising a diverse range of facilities including teaching spaces, laboratories, administrative buildings, libraries, plant rooms and specialist research environments. <br /><br />Mechanical services systems across these facilities include heating, ventilation and air conditioning (HVAC) plant and associated infrastructure necessary to maintain appropriate environmental conditions within University buildings. <br /><br />The preventative maintenance services specified within this tender apply to nominated buildings and mechanical services assets across Federation University campuses. <br /><br />Exclusion: BMS Services are out of scope and are not included as part of this tender.<br /><br />Please ensure that all files attached to this tender are responded to as required.<br /><br />Mandatory Site Visits<br /><br />Attendance at the mandatory site visit is a requirement of this tender process. Respondents must register their intention to attend by submi...<br /><br /><b>Issued by : </b> Federation University<br /><b>Closing Date</b> : 10/Jul/2026 05:00 PM (UTC+10:00) Canberra, Melbourne, Sydney time<br /><b>Reference number</b> : VP509397<br /><b>Contact person</b> : Not disclosed<br /><b>Tender categories</b> : Building Trade, Repairs, Maint., Construction & Operation, Mechanical Plant, Equip, Services<br /><b>Specification Docs</b> : 19]]></description>
