<item><title>CQUEOI-26-21-DFM - CTL Student Accommodation</title>
<description><![CDATA[<b>Tender Details : </b> CQUniversity Australia (CQUniversity) is seeking Expressions of Interest (EOI) from suitably qualified and experienced developers, investors, and operators to design, develop, deliver and/or operate purpose-built student accommodation to support the growing student demand at its campuses in regional Queensland.<br /><br />CQUniversity is open to traditional and innovative commercial, delivery and operating models, and encourages proponents to propose solutions that are financially sustainable, student-centred, and operationally efficient.<br /><br />This EOI is intended to approach the market and seek information to allow the University to realistically consider available options to finalise a potential preferred approach to student accommodation provision, particularly at its Mackay and Bundaberg campuses, although we are also interested in expanding student accommodation across our entire regional footprint.<br /><br />For detailed information on the specific services sought under this tender, please review...<br /><br /><b>Issued by : </b> Central Queensland University<br /><b>Closing Date</b> : 10/Jul/2026 12:00 PM (UTC+10:00) Brisbane time<br /><b>Reference number</b> : VP509751<br /><b>Contact person</b> : Not disclosed<br /><b>Tender categories</b> : Architecture, Design, Planning, Business & Administrative Services, Community & Social Services, Construction & Operation, Management Advisory Services, Real Estate & Property Services<br /><b>Specification Docs</b> : 2]]></description>
