<item><title>Provision of Prepaid Card Services Solution</title>
<description><![CDATA[<b>Tender Details : </b> The Public Trustee of Queensland (QPT) is seeking to establish a multi-year arrangement with a suitably qualified supplier for the provision of a prepaid card services solution to support customer expenditure under approved budgets. The appointed supplier will work collaboratively with QPT to deliver a secure, cost effective, and user friendly spend management solution that meets the needs of some of Queensland’s most vulnerable customers.<br /><br />QPT seeks a supplier that can:<br /><br />•	provide dedicated account management and responsive support services<br /><br />•	demonstrate a strong understanding of QPT’s operating environment and the customers we support<br /><br />•	deliver intuitive, reliable systems—such as a secure web-based administration portal—to enable effective management of prepaid card services<br /><br />•	work collaboratively with QPT to drive continuous improvement and process efficiency<br /><br />•	provide a pricing model that supports low cost operation and safeguards customer fu...<br /><br /><b>Issued by : </b> Queensland Public Trustee<br /><b>Closing Date</b> : 13/Jul/2026 02:00 PM (UTC+10:00) Brisbane time<br /><b>Reference number</b> : VP509435<br /><b>Contact person</b> : Not disclosed<br /><b>Tender categories</b> : Financial & Insurance Services, IT & Telecomms<br /><b>Specification Docs</b> : 5]]></description>
