<item><title>Queensland Government - Preferred Supplier Panel for Grocery, Dairy and Beverages</title>
<description><![CDATA[<b>Tender Details : </b> Queensland Government is seeking applications from Suppliers who wish to register to be a Preferred Supplier for Grocery, Dairy and Beverage Products. This is a follow on from the initial application request period released on QTenders in March 2021 (HSQ101256). As part of this Preferred Supplier Panel we are accepting supplier applications at any time. Suppliers who have submitted an application via the initial registration process (HSQ101256) do not need to resubmit an application.<br /><br />The Preferred Supplier Panel categories include:<br /><br />Grocery Products Dry Goods<br /><br />Biscuits; baking mixes and supplies; flour and milled products; soups; stocks; powders; packaged desserts; savoury snacks; confectionary; nuts; grains; legumes; jelly; spreads; jams; preserves; sugar; sweetener; dry pasta; rice; noodles; cereals; oats; porridge; pulses; seasoning; dried herbs; spices; sauces; dressing; canned goods; vinegar; condiments; dried fruit; dried vegetables; fruit cups pureed fruit.<br /><br />Fro...<br /><br /><b>Issued by : </b> Queensland Health<br /><b>Closing Date</b> : 31/Jan/2027 05:00 PM (UTC+10:00) Brisbane time<br /><b>Reference number</b> : VP465869<br /><b>Contact person</b> : Not disclosed<br /><b>Tender categories</b> : Food & Beverage Products<br /><b>Specification Docs</b> : 4]]></description>
